<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>我的第一個網頁</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f0f8ff;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 50px;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #2c3e50;
    }
    button {
      padding: 10px 20px;
      font-size: 16px;
      background-color: #3498db;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    button:hover {
      background-color: #2980b9;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>歡迎來到我的網頁！</h1>
  <p>這是一個簡單的 HTML 範例。</p>
  <button onclick="showMessage()">點我一下</button>

  <script>
    function showMessage() {
      alert("你好！這是 JavaScript 的提示訊息。");
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>

